sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Ingress<br/>(Gateway API / Istio)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant VLLM as vLLM Container<br/>(odh-vllm-cuda-rhel9)<br/>8000/TCP HTTP, 8033/TCP gRPC
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA API
    participant HFHub as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PVC as PVC Volume<br/>Filesystem

    Note over VLLM,GPU: Flow 2: Model Loading at Startup

    alt Model from PVC
        PVC->>VLLM: Read model weights<br/>Filesystem mount
    else Model from S3
        VLLM->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: IAM/access key
        S3-->>VLLM: Model weights
    else Model from Hugging Face
        VLLM->>HFHub: GET model weights + tokenizer<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
        HFHub-->>VLLM: Model artifacts
    end

    VLLM->>GPU: Transfer model weights<br/>CUDA API
    Note over VLLM,GPU: Model loaded to GPU memory

    Note over Client,VLLM: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (HTTP)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS<br/>JWT validation
    KRBP->>VLLM: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000 (plaintext localhost)<br/>No auth (already validated)
    VLLM->>GPU: Run inference<br/>CUDA API
    GPU-->>VLLM: Inference result
    VLLM-->>KRBP: JSON response<br/>HTTP/8000
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response<br/>HTTPS/8443
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client,VLLM: Flow 1b: Model Inference Request (gRPC / TGIS)

    Client->>Gateway: gRPC GenerationService call<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.3<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward gRPC<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS
    KRBP->>VLLM: Forward gRPC<br/>gRPC/8033 (plaintext)<br/>No auth
    VLLM->>GPU: Run inference<br/>CUDA API
    GPU-->>VLLM: Inference result
    VLLM-->>KRBP: gRPC response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response
